  traitJob: Bunker Enthusiast
  traitCauseOfDeath: Forgot the combination to his own airtight bunker lock and suffocated
    outside it
  traitPersonality: Paranoid, conspiratorial, bitter that the world didn't actually
    end when he predicted it
  characterSin: 2
