  propMaterialOverrides: []
  introLines:
  - I knew it! The government grid finally collapsed!
  - Where are your hazmat suits? This radiation level must be off the charts
  answerWhatHappenedBefore: I heard a loud thud outside, thought the apocalypse had
    finally arrived, ran to my bunker, but blanked on my password. The airtight seals
    locked me out instead of in
  answerWhatKindOfLife: A watchful one. While my neighbors wasted their money on
    vacations and nice cars, I spent every penny on canned beans and ammo
  answerWhatWasYourJob: I was a self-employed tactical survival consultant. Mostly
    I just made online videos lecturing people about the end times
  answerWhatHappenedClothes: My shirt is rumpled and sweaty from spending twelve
    hours scratching the steel door of my bunker trying to guess my birthday backwards
  answerWhyHaveItem: A survivalist always keeps an axe handy. It's for clearing debris,
    gathering timber, or dealing with mutant raiders
